[{"id": 260753, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 562, "ruku": 496, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5242, "text": "BENDITO Aquel en cuya mano est\u00e1 toda la soberan\u00eda, pues s\u00f3lo \u00c9l tiene poder para disponer cualquier cosa:"}, {"id": 260754, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 562, "ruku": 496, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5243, "text": "Aquel que ha creado la muerte y la vida, para probaros [y as\u00ed poner de manifiesto] qui\u00e9n observa la mejor conducta, y [haceros ver que] \u00c9l solo es todopoderoso, realmente indulgente."}, {"id": 260755, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 562, "ruku": 496, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5244, "text": "[Bendito] Aquel que ha creado siete cielos en perfecta armon\u00eda entre s\u00ed: no hallar\u00e1s el menor fallo en la creaci\u00f3n del M\u00e1s Misericordioso. Mira de nuevo: \u00bfpuedes ver alguna fisura?"}, {"id": 260756, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 562, "ruku": 496, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5245, "text": "Si, mira de nuevo, una y otra vez: [y cada vez] tu vista volver\u00e1 a ti, deslumbrada y realmente vencida...."}, {"id": 260757, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 562, "ruku": 496, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5246, "text": "Y, en verdad, hemos adornado el cielo m\u00e1s pr\u00f3ximo a la tierra con luceros, y los hemos hecho objeto de conjeturas para los [hombres] malvados: y para ellos hemos preparado el castigo de las llamas abrasadoras \u2013"}, {"id": 260758, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 562, "ruku": 496, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5247, "text": "pues, a quienes se empe\u00f1an en blasfemar [de esa forma] contra su Sustentador les aguarda el castigo del infierno: \u00a1qu\u00e9 horrible destino!"}, {"id": 260759, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 562, "ruku": 496, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5248, "text": "Cuando sean arrojados en ese [infierno], oir\u00e1n su fragor mientras hierve,"}, {"id": 260760, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 562, "ruku": 496, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5249, "text": "a punto de estallar de furia; [y] cada vez que un grupo [de esos pecadores] es arrojado en \u00e9l, sus guardianes les preguntan: \u201c\u00bfNo vino a vosotros ning\u00fan advertidor?\u201d"}, {"id": 260761, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 562, "ruku": 496, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5250, "text": "Responder\u00e1n: \u201cSi, en verdad; vino a nosotros un advertidor pero le tachamos de mentiroso y dijimos: \u2018\u00a1Dios nunca ha hecho descender nada [como revelaci\u00f3n]! \u00a1Ciertamente, vosotros [que os dec\u00eds advertidores] no sois sino v\u00edctimas de un gran enga\u00f1o!\u2019\u201d"}, {"id": 260762, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 562, "ruku": 496, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5251, "text": "Y a\u00f1adir\u00e1n: \u201c\u00a1Si hubi\u00e9ramos escuchado [esas advertencias], o hubi\u00e9ramos [al menos] hecho uso de la raz\u00f3n, no estar\u00edamos [ahora] entre los que est\u00e1n destinados a las llamas abrasadoras!\u201d"}, {"id": 260763, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 562, "ruku": 496, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5252, "text": "Entonces reconocer\u00e1n sus pecados: pero todo bien estar\u00e1 [ya] fuera del alcance de los que est\u00e1n destinados a las llamas abrasadoras."}, {"id": 260764, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 562, "ruku": 496, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5253, "text": "[En cambio,] ciertamente, para los que temen a su Sustentador aun estando \u00c9l fuera del alcance de su percepci\u00f3n, habr\u00e1 perd\u00f3n y una gran recompensa."}, {"id": 260765, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 563, "ruku": 496, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5254, "text": "Y [SABED, Oh hombres, que] tanto si ocult\u00e1is vuestras creencias como si las declar\u00e1is p\u00fablicamente, \u00c9l tiene en verdad pleno conocimiento de lo que hay en [vuestros] corazones."}, {"id": 260766, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 563, "ruku": 496, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5255, "text": "\u00bfC\u00f3mo es posible que Aquel que ha creado [todo] no sepa [todo]? \u00a1Si, s\u00f3lo \u00c9l es inescrutable [en Su sabidur\u00eda], consciente de todo!"}, {"id": 260768, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 563, "ruku": 497, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5256, "text": "\u00c9l es quien os ha hecho la tierra f\u00e1cil de habitar: viajad, pues, por todas sus regiones, y comed del sustento que \u00c9l os da: pero [tened siempre presente que] ser\u00e9is resucitados para [comparecer ante] \u00c9l."}, {"id": 260769, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 563, "ruku": 497, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5257, "text": "\u00bfPod\u00e9is sentiros jam\u00e1s seguros de que Aquel que est\u00e1 en el cielo no haga que os trague la tierra cuando, de repente, comienza a temblar?"}, {"id": 260770, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 563, "ruku": 497, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5258, "text": "\u00bfO pod\u00e9is sentiros jam\u00e1s seguros de que Aquel que est\u00e1 en el cielo no env\u00ede contra vosotros una tormenta devastadora, y entonces sabr\u00edais qu\u00e9 [real] era Mi advertencia?"}, {"id": 260771, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 563, "ruku": 497, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5259, "text": "Y, en verdad, [muchos de] los que vivieron con anterioridad tacharon de mentira [Mis advertencias]: \u00a1y qu\u00e9 terrible fue Mi reprobaci\u00f3n [de ellos]!"}, {"id": 260772, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 563, "ruku": 497, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5260, "text": "\u00bfNo han visto a las aves [volando] por encima de ellos, extendiendo y replegando sus alas? Nadie sino el M\u00e1s Misericordioso las mantiene en vuelo: realmente, \u00c9l ve todas las cosas."}, {"id": 260773, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 563, "ruku": 497, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5261, "text": "\u00bfY quien hay, aparte del M\u00e1s Misericordioso, que pueda ser un escudo para vosotros, y pueda auxiliaros [en el peligro]? \u00a1Quienes niegan esta verdad est\u00e1n sumidos en un autoenga\u00f1o!"}, {"id": 260774, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 563, "ruku": 497, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5262, "text": "\u00bfO qui\u00e9n hay que pueda daros el sustento si \u00c9l [os] suspende Su provisi\u00f3n? \u00a1Pero, aun as\u00ed, [los que se empe\u00f1an en negar la verdad] persisten tercamente en su desd\u00e9n [por los mensajes de Dios] y en su ciega huida [de \u00c9l]!"}, {"id": 260775, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 563, "ruku": 497, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5263, "text": "\u00bfEst\u00e1, acaso, quien marcha con el rostro pegado al suelo mejor dirigido que quien marcha erguido por un camino recto?"}, {"id": 260776, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 563, "ruku": 497, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5264, "text": "DI: \u201c\u00c9l es quien os ha creado [a todos], y os ha dotado de o\u00eddo, de vista y de mentes: [sin embargo,] \u00a1qu\u00e9 raras veces sois agradecidos!\u201d"}, {"id": 260617, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 563, "ruku": 497, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5265, "text": "Di: \u201c\u00c9l es quien ha hecho que os multipliqu\u00e9is en la tierra; y ante \u00c9l ser\u00e9is congregados.\u201d"}, {"id": 260777, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 563, "ruku": 497, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5266, "text": "Pero [tan s\u00f3lo] preguntan: \u201c\u00bfCu\u00e1ndo se cumplir\u00e1 esa promesa? \u00a1[Responded a esto, Oh vosotros que cre\u00e9is en ella,] si sois veraces!\u201d"}, {"id": 260778, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 563, "ruku": 497, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5267, "text": "Di [Oh Profeta]: \u201cEl conocimiento de eso pertenece s\u00f3lo a Dios; y yo soy solamente un advertidor claro.\u201d"}, {"id": 260779, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 564, "ruku": 497, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5268, "text": "Pero al final, cuando vean inminente ese [cumplimiento], los rostros de aquellos que se empe\u00f1aron en negar la verdad quedar\u00e1n consternados; y se les dir\u00e1: \u201c\u00a1Esto es lo que [con tanta burla] reclamabais!\u201d"}, {"id": 260780, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 564, "ruku": 497, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5269, "text": "DI [Oh Profeta]: \u201c\u00bfQu\u00e9 os parece? Si Dios me hace perecer a m\u00ed y a los que me siguen, o nos favorece con Su gracia --\u00bfhay alguien que pueda proteger a los que [como vosotros] niegan la verdad de un castigo doloroso [en la Otra Vida]?\u201d"}, {"id": 260781, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 564, "ruku": 497, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5270, "text": "Di: \u201c\u00c9l es el M\u00e1s Misericordioso: en \u00c9l creemos y en \u00c9l hemos puesto nuestra confianza; y en su momento habr\u00e9is de saber qui\u00e9n de nosotros estaba claramente extraviado.\u201d"}, {"id": 260782, "identifier": "es.asad", "surah_number": 67, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0644\u0643", "surah_en_name": "Al-Mulk", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Sovereignty", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 29, "manzil": 7, "page": 564, "ruku": 497, "hizb_quarter": 225, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "es", "name": "Asad", "transelator_en_name": "Muhammad Asad - Abdurrasak P\u00e9rez", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5271, "text": "Di [a esos que niegan la verdad]: \u201c\u00bfQu\u00e9 os parece? Si toda vuestra agua desapareciera de repente bajo la tierra, \u00bfqui\u00e9n [sino Dios] podr\u00eda proveeros de agua de [nuevos] manantiales puros?\u201d"}]